*[dir='ltr'] { direction:ltr; unicode-bidi:embed; }
*[dir='lro'] { direction:ltr; unicode-bidi:bidi-override; }

body.example:
To show all entities in the Author mode as transparent, without
      a gray background, first define in your CSS after all imports the
      namespace:@namespace oxy "http://www.oxygenxml.com/extensions/author";and
      then add the following
      selector:oxy|entity {
    background-color: inherit !important;
}
